title: CROSSED - BADLANDS 039 (2013) (4 Covers) (Darkness-Empire)
description:
CROSSED BADLANDS #39
(Mature Readers)

Publisher: AVATAR PRESS INC
(Writer) Simon Spurrier (Artist/Cover Artist) Rafael Ortiz

The ultimate '70s grindhouse showdown is here! Murdering bikers! Stoned junkies! And a whole mess of diabolical Crossed, bring this story to an explosive, violent, and horrifying end. Three very different people come together to exact vengeance and meet their bloody fates. SIMON SPURRIER delivers the concluding issue of the "American Quitters" arc with a shocking and miserable finale that will leave you emotionally exhausted. Available with a Regular, Torture, Wraparound, and special Red Crossed Incentive covers by Rafael Ortiz.  

In Shops: 10/16/2013
